Defendant Salah I. Salahadyn in court with attorney Richard Henry Hart.  Defendant Salah I. Salahadyn in custody.  David Robles appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Sentencing proceeded.  Statements by the State, defense and defendant.  Additional statements by:  Mr. Frank A.  The Court imposed the following sentence:

Defendant's TOTAL LENGTH OF SENTENCE shall be 12 years. Defendant's TERM OF CONFINEMENT in the Wisconsin Prison System shall be for 7 years   with credit for 52 days time served.  Defendant shall serve 5 years   on EXTENDED SUPERVISION.    The defendant is not eligible for the Challenge Incarceration Program or the Wisconsin Substance Abuse Program.  The Court advised the defendant of his determinate sentence pursuant to statute and in accordance with Form CR-234.  Copy provided to defendant. 
 * Pay restitution (to be argued a later restitution hearing), plus DNA surcharge, all costs and disbursements, with the restitution to be paid first.  Cash bail on deposit to apply.  Balance to be paid from prison funds.

CONDITIONS OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION:
 - No contact with the victim, Frank A., or his family, their residence or place(s) of employment;
 - No contact with Universal Allah;
 - Undergo a mental health assessment; follow any treatment recommended;
 - Remain alcohol free;
 - Remain free of controlled substances other than those legally prescribed for defendant by a duly licensed physician for his mental or physical needs; take as prescribed and only for as long as deemed medically reasonable and necessary;
 - AODA assessment; treatment if needed;
 - Urine screens;
 - Cognitive thinking intervention counseling;
 - Seek and maintain employment;
 - Be given job and vocational training;
 - Parenting classes/counseling.  
 - Pay any balances remaining of the DNA surcharge, restitution (once ordered) costs and disbursements.  Failure to pay would result in a civil judgment entered against defendant.

Court set matter for restiution hearing on 12/18/14 at 3:00 p.m.  Defendant to appear by video; video technician is available on that date.

